' ============================================================
' HRMS 核心業務循序圖 (4 個場景)
' 渲染指令：java -jar tools/plantuml.jar -smetana -o diagrams 01_核心業務循序圖.puml
' ============================================================

' ---- 場景一：新進員工入職流程 ----
@startuml 01_員工入職流程
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft JhengHei"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 新進員工入職流程 (Employee Onboarding)

actor "人資/管理員(UI)" as HR
participant "ORG 微服務\n(Organization)" as ORG
database "ORG 資料庫" as DB_ORG
queue "Kafka\n(Event Bus)" as Kafka
participant "IAM 微服務\n(身份認證)" as IAM
participant "INS 微服務\n(勞健保)" as INS
participant "PAY 微服務\n(薪資)" as PAY
participant "NTF 微服務\n(通知服務)" as NTF

== Phase 1: 同步寫入與事件發布 (Synchronous) ==

HR -> ORG : POST /api/v1/employees\n(新增員工資料)
activate ORG
ORG -> ORG : 驗證必填欄位與格式\n(Business Validation)
ORG -> DB_ORG : INSERT 員工基本資料\n(State Change)
DB_ORG --> ORG : 寫入成功 (Return ID)
ORG -> Kafka : Publish: EmployeeCreatedEvent\n{empId, name, email, deptId}
note right of ORG : 遵循 Outbox Pattern\n確保事件不遺失
ORG --> HR : HTTP 200 OK (建檔完成)
note left of ORG : HR 無須等待後續流程\n前端畫面瞬間收到成功回饋
deactivate ORG

== Phase 2: 非同步業務處理 (Asynchronous Pub/Sub) ==

par 並發處理
  Kafka --> IAM : Consume: EmployeeCreatedEvent
  activate IAM
  IAM -> IAM : 產生系統預設密碼\n綁定基礎 Role
  IAM -> IAM : 寫入 IAM Schema\n(帳號就緒)
  deactivate IAM
else 保險投保
  Kafka --> INS : Consume: EmployeeCreatedEvent
  activate INS
  INS -> INS : 產生預設勞健保級距檔案
  INS -> INS : 寫入 INS Schema\n(待 HR 呈報)
  deactivate INS
else 薪資建檔
  Kafka --> PAY : Consume: EmployeeCreatedEvent
  activate PAY
  PAY -> PAY : 產生空白計薪結構\n與預設薪資帳戶格式
  PAY -> PAY : 寫入 PAY Schema
  deactivate PAY
else 發送歡迎信
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: EmployeeCreatedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF -> NTF : 渲染 Email 版面
  NTF --> HR : 寄送「歡迎入職與登入密碼信」
  deactivate NTF
end

@enduml

' ---- 場景二：請假簽核流程 ----
@startuml 01_請假簽核流程
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft JhengHei"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 請假簽核流程 (Leave Approval Flow)

actor "員工(UI)" as Emp
participant "ATT 微服務\n(考勤)" as ATT
database "ATT 資料庫" as DB_ATT
queue "Kafka\n(Event Bus)" as Kafka
participant "WFL 微服務\n(工作流引擎)" as WFL
participant "NTF 微服務\n(通知)" as NTF
actor "直屬主管(UI)" as Mgr

== Phase 1: 提交申請 & 暫凍餘額 (Synchronous) ==

Emp -> ATT : POST /api/v1/leaves\n{type: 特休, startDate, endDate}
activate ATT
ATT -> ATT : 驗證：餘額充足？\n時段不衝突？
ATT -> DB_ATT : INSERT leave_requests\n(status: PENDING_APPROVAL)\nUPDATE leave_balances\n(暫凍對應時數)
DB_ATT --> ATT : 寫入成功
ATT -> Kafka : Publish: LeaveRequestCreatedEvent\n{requestId, empId, type, hours, managerId}
ATT --> Emp : HTTP 200 OK\n(申請已送出，等待主管審核)
deactivate ATT

== Phase 2: 簽核任務指派 (Asynchronous) ==

par 建立簽核任務
  Kafka --> WFL : Consume: LeaveRequestCreatedEvent
  activate WFL
  WFL -> WFL : 依流程定義建立 WorkflowInstance\n指派 ApprovalTask 給 managerId
  deactivate WFL
else 通知主管
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: LeaveRequestCreatedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF --> Mgr : 推送簽核通知\n(站內信 + Email)
  deactivate NTF
end

== Phase 3: 主管審核 (Decision) ==

Mgr -> WFL : PUT /api/v1/workflow/tasks/{taskId}/approve\n{decision: APPROVED, comment: "同意"}
activate WFL

alt 核准 (Approved)
  WFL -> Kafka : Publish: LeaveApprovedEvent\n{requestId, empId, hours}
  deactivate WFL
  Kafka --> ATT : Consume: LeaveApprovedEvent
  activate ATT
  ATT -> DB_ATT : UPDATE leave_requests\n(status: APPROVED)\n確認扣除假期餘額\n(暫凍轉正式扣除)
  deactivate ATT
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: LeaveApprovedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF --> Emp : 通知員工：請假已核准
  deactivate NTF

else 駁回 (Rejected)
  WFL -> Kafka : Publish: LeaveRejectedEvent\n{requestId, empId, hours, reason}
  Kafka --> ATT : Consume: LeaveRejectedEvent
  activate ATT
  ATT -> DB_ATT : UPDATE leave_requests\n(status: REJECTED)\n還原暫凍的假期餘額
  deactivate ATT
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: LeaveRejectedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF --> Emp : 通知員工：請假已駁回（含原因）
  deactivate NTF
end

@enduml

' ---- 場景三：薪資月結 SAGA 補償流程 ----
@startuml 01_薪資SAGA補償流程
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft JhengHei"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 薪資月結 SAGA 補償流程 (Payroll Monthly Run with SAGA)

actor "人資管理員(UI)" as HR
participant "PAY 微服務\n(薪資結算)" as PAY
database "PAY 資料庫" as DB_PAY
participant "ATT 微服務\n(考勤)" as ATT
participant "INS 微服務\n(勞健保)" as INS
queue "Kafka\n(Event Bus)" as Kafka
participant "NTF 微服務\n(通知)" as NTF

== SAGA Step 1~3：啟動結算 & 跨服務資料聚合 ==

HR -> PAY : POST /api/v1/payroll/runs\n{year: 2026, month: 2}
activate PAY
PAY -> DB_PAY : INSERT payroll_runs\n(status: PROCESSING)
DB_PAY --> PAY : OK (runId: R2026-02)
PAY --> HR : HTTP 202 Accepted\n(結算進行中)

note over PAY, INS : SAGA Step 2:\nAPI Composition 聚合各服務資料
PAY -> ATT : GET /api/v1/attendance/monthly-summary\n?month=2026-02
ATT --> PAY : 全員考勤摘要\n(出勤天數、加班時數、請假扣薪)
PAY -> INS : GET /api/v1/insurance/monthly-contributions\n?month=2026-02
INS --> PAY : 全員保費自付額清單\n(勞保 + 健保 + 勞退)

== SAGA Step 4~6：計算、鎖定與完成 ==

PAY -> PAY : 依序計算每位員工淨薪\n(底薪 + 加給 + 加班費\n- 請假扣薪 - 保費 - 預扣稅)

alt SAGA 成功路徑 (All Steps Pass)
  PAY -> DB_PAY : UPDATE payroll_runs\n(status: LOCKED)\nBULK INSERT payroll_items\n(每位員工明細)
  PAY -> PAY : 產出銀行轉帳媒體檔\n(TXT/CSV)
  PAY -> Kafka : Publish: PayrollCompletedEvent\n{runId, month, totalNetPay}
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: PayrollCompletedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF -> NTF : 產生個人電子薪資單 PDF
  NTF -> NTF : 寄送薪資單通知給全體員工
  deactivate NTF
  PAY --> HR : 結算完成\n(含媒體檔下載連結)

else SAGA 補償路徑 (Compensating Transaction)
  note over PAY : 計算失敗\n(如：某員工薪資結構異常)
  PAY -> DB_PAY : UPDATE payroll_runs\n(status: FAILED)\nDELETE 本次已寫入的\n中間計算資料（補償回滾）
  PAY -> Kafka : Publish: PayrollFailedEvent\n{runId, failedStep, errorDetail}
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: PayrollFailedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF --> HR : 緊急警示通知\n(結算失敗 + 錯誤明細)
  deactivate NTF
  note over PAY : 資料庫回到結算前的乾淨狀態\nHR 修正錯誤後可重新觸發結算
end

deactivate PAY

@enduml

' ---- 場景四：員工離職流程 ----
@startuml 01_員工離職流程
!theme plain
skinparam defaultFontName "Microsoft JhengHei"
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center
title 員工離職流程 (Employee Offboarding Flow)

actor "人資管理員(UI)" as HR
participant "ORG 微服務\n(組織員工)" as ORG
database "ORG 資料庫" as DB_ORG
queue "Kafka\n(Event Bus)" as Kafka
participant "IAM 微服務\n(身份認證)" as IAM
participant "INS 微服務\n(勞健保)" as INS
participant "PAY 微服務\n(薪資)" as PAY
participant "NTF 微服務\n(通知)" as NTF

== Phase 1: 離職建檔 & 事件發布 (Synchronous) ==

HR -> ORG : POST /api/v1/employees/{id}/offboard\n{terminationDate, reason, handoverTo}
activate ORG
ORG -> ORG : 前置檢查：確認無未結清的代墊款\n無進行中的待審核表單
ORG -> DB_ORG : UPDATE employees\n(status: TERMINATED, terminationDate)\nINSERT offboarding_records\n(交接人、離職原因)
DB_ORG --> ORG : 寫入成功
ORG -> Kafka : Publish: EmployeeTerminatedEvent\n{empId, terminationDate, remainingLeaveDays}
ORG --> HR : HTTP 200 OK (離職手續完成)
note left of ORG : HR 無須等待帳號停用\n退保等後續流程即可完成操作
deactivate ORG

== Phase 2: 非同步自動化離職作業 (Asynchronous Pub/Sub) ==

par 帳號排程停用
  Kafka --> IAM : Consume: EmployeeTerminatedEvent
  activate IAM
  IAM -> IAM : 設定帳號停用排程\n(生效時間 = terminationDate 23:59)
  note right of IAM : 允許員工在離職日當天\n仍可正常使用系統
  deactivate IAM
else 勞健保退保
  Kafka --> INS : Consume: EmployeeTerminatedEvent
  activate INS
  INS -> INS : 建立退保申請記錄\n(退保日 = terminationDate)
  INS -> INS : 計算最後一個月保費（按比例）
  deactivate INS
else 最終薪資結算
  Kafka --> PAY : Consume: EmployeeTerminatedEvent
  activate PAY
  PAY -> PAY : 計算未休特休折現金額\n(remainingLeaveDays × 日薪)
  PAY -> PAY : 標記該員工於下次月結時\n納入離職月份最終薪資計算
  deactivate PAY
else 寄送離職通知
  Kafka --> NTF : Consume: EmployeeTerminatedEvent
  activate NTF
  NTF --> HR : 離職辦理完成確認單\n(含交接清單)
  NTF -> NTF : 寄送離職感謝信給員工
  deactivate NTF
end

@enduml
